reviews.review_text: AWESOME Listening to it now on my 3.1 computer speaker. Feels like you are in the crowd, great recording. Nice and clear, arena reverb is a little much but that's how an arena can sound. Thanks for the 24bit rip. Crowd seems polite so far. Sounds like a happy and creative night for the band. Phil is rumbling, Bobby seems to be going for it. Jerry is definitely feeling it. Love Estimated Prophet especially the end. RECOMMENDED.
